Invocation Name: cloud flashcards
des:
Learn and practice cloud web services interactively to get basic information about each services in cloud. 

Alexa can help you learn cloud services or study for your test. You can review the flash cards and then test your knowledge. At any point you can say "Alexa, review mode" to switch to review or say "Alexa, test mode" to start a test. You can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next card. At any point during the test, you can say "Alexa, what's my score" to get your current test score.
